{"tid":2373246,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：民主派區佬製破格banner  自由欄杆變藝術裝置（李八方）","createTime":"2021-01-20T09:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T10:01:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70c9fe61d32b83561b7ea12a056e55fc40aa248e","tid":2373246,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/4DXIPSRB7JCA7BNG4YTXVNIYPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2F4DXIPSRB7JCA7BNG4YTXVNIYPQ%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IaxUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=925e1ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2F4DXIPSRB7JCA7BNG4YTXVNIYPQ%2F&h=1cd39aa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/4DXIPSRB7JCA7BNG4YTXVNIYPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：民主派區佬製破格banner <br />\n自由欄杆變藝術裝置（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oCZgN2hoFH4UKt2SpainJmy0Qo4=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7NGTPYWE3NF6PF3D4HYRE45AYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoCZgN2hoFH4UKt2SpainJmy0Qo4%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7NGTPYWE3NF6PF3D4HYRE45AYQ.jpg&h=53552659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳敬倫喺區議員橫額位置用木板將自由二字設計成「鐵窗」般嘅裝置藝術。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員陳敬倫近日利用木板同鐵欄，喺區議員橫額位置用自由二字設計成「鐵窗」般嘅裝置藝術，一方面防止建制嘅人玩撕banner，一方面用藝術發聲，創意引來唔少網民share，不過呢個只係陳敬倫創作嘅開始，之後好嘢跟住嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靈感源自建制「坐晒監」<br />\n<br />\n民主派區議員橫額常被破壞塗污，今次陳敬倫以幾塊貼咗黑色膠紙嘅木板，結合貼咗黑色膠紙嘅欄杆，打直睇係「二三」，打橫睇係「自由」，八方睇到「頭已側」。<br />\n<br />\n陳敬倫話設計靈感來自以往從背面睇住被太陽曬住嘅建制派橫額，好似呈現出個個坐晒監嘅樣。佢決定用幾塊長且窄嘅木板，再用衣架鐵線固定喺鐵欄上，要拆落嚟唔容易，目的係測試一下係廢老、大媽即興清橫額，抑或破壞者係有預謀。至於整個裝置想表達咩意思，陳敬倫話相信大家「明就明」。<br />\n<br />\n陳仲話︰「大家都好有反應，可能因為最近冇乜其他新文宣。好開心見到有人喺欄杆影相打卡。可能大家覺得，我哋想要嘅係好簡單好基本，點解個政治環境要咁樣呢？」陳敬倫同八方透露，下周將有第二個裝置面世，同樣係欄杆上嘅新字樣，之後仲會有其他設計。<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/844qWsDJFXqcnwZ48Qv8nutJCr0=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YVFJWOIVTBC63JP7JW43LZDTKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F844qWsDJFXqcnwZ48Qv8nutJCr0%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYVFJWOIVTBC63JP7JW43LZDTKM.jpg&h=8da7d5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳敬倫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gjLjKEiDqodDGePBHN5XjfHjqXE=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AWRNVGY6ONCE3KOYOU55JHVMIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgjLjKEiDqodDGePBHN5XjfHjqXE%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAWRNVGY6ONCE3KOYOU55JHVMIY.jpg&h=ac629a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■木板用鐵線固定喺鐵欄上， 防止藍絲破壞。"},{"pid":"d7db00e6730c5ab8760f6f83c0544488b4be721e","tid":2373246,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"其實你唔講，班藍屎邊會知係自由，唔知就唔會破壞架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}